taining a portfolio of REITs, like Vanguard&#8217;s REIT ETF. Publicly trad=
ed REITs appear to be low fee, but by the time it gets to you, many parties=
 will have taken cuts for their piece of the process, from sourcing to mana=
gement.&nbsp;</p></li></ol><p style=3D"color: #1a1a1a; font-size: 16px; lin=
