 from retail investors like me and handles the whole real estate investment=
 process, from sourcing to rehab to management, using technology to remove =
layers and lower fees.</p><p style=3D"color: #1a1a1a; font-size: 16px; line=
-height: 26px; margin: 0 0 1em 0;">Here&#8217;s how it works. Investors go =
